dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Map shows four classes of roads, European routes, route numbers, distances in kilometers, car ferries, national borders. Verso: Inset map "Athinai" and distance table. On back cover: "Kalos ēlthate stēn 'Texaco' : diethnēs emporikē drastēriotēs." "Καλώς ήλθατε στην 'Texaco' : Διεθνής εμπορική δραστηριότης."
